title: Opie & Jim Norton JUN 30 2015 Tue.mp3
description:
THANKS TO @SternGeek FOR THE FILE


On Today's Show: Dan Soder, Amy Schumer, Sherrod Small.

With Jim Norton out, we start the show with Sherrod Small in studio, we talk about Erik and Gittles in Miami, Sherrod wants Red Eye to pay him, we discuss the escaped prisoners, we talk about Caitlyn Jenner, and Opie sees a documentary about Amy Winehouse. 

Dan Soder joins the show, we talk more about Caitlyn Jenner, and NBC fires Donald Trump. 

Dennis Falcone stops by with a gift for Sherrod, and Amy Schumer stops by to promote Trainwreck. 

We recap our time with Amy, CNN mistakes a dildo flag for an ISIS flag, Walmart makes an ISIS cake, we talk about Bernie Goetz, and we wrap up with Dan and Sherrod
